Web Trek 
(C) 2012 Kyle Delaney
Free software under the terms of the BSD Two-Clause license, see COPYING for 
details.

A free web-based implementation of the classic Star Trek-inspired Basic game.

I refered to the following for gameplay details:
* Super Star Trek (C) David Ahl 1978
* Super Star Trek Classic (v1.1) (C) 1996 Chris Nystrom

Notes:
* Damage effects are not currently implemented for anything but engines and the
  Engineering department.
* The win condition is not yet recognized, but you'll know when you hit 0 
  klingons.